properties.title: PY08 Sri Damansara Timur

properties.comment:
• A huge highway prevents pedestrian access from neighborhoods north of the station.
  • South of the station, the situation is less grim, although there is room for improvement, e.g. by setting up pedestrian walkways and dedicated bike lanes.

properties.title: PY03 Kampung Selamat
properties.comment: Easy access for workers of industrial area west of the station. Kampung Selamat to the east should have better access. Furthermore a footbridge over Lebuhraya Utara–Selatan would allow thousands apartment residents to quickly reach the MRT station on foot or by bike

properties.title: PY38 16 Sierra
properties.comment:

The so far unbuilt land presents a unique opportunity to develop a high-density, car-independent neighborhood, where all essential amenities are conveniently accessible by walking or cycling.

properties.title: PY24 Chan Sow Lin
